{"tid":611169,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門新福利有本地人站長以工作期間於站長室內為理由被解僱 ，但同時於中國引入外勞","createTime":"2018-03-30T16:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T13:17:39.000Z","uid":20058,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5e80a0acc3399c6cede5eafaa7db6259c7b37009","tid":611169,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T16:51:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/macaubus/posts/10156199360239520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmacaubus%2Fposts%2F10156199360239520&d=1rRYkwox2c35Iw131GJFouargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=799dbb1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/macaubus/posts/10156199360239520</a>有多位新福利站長向本專頁表示，近期接獲公司發出的「警告信」，警告原因竟是「站長在工作時間留在站長室內」，而更有站長因收兩封警告信後，獲管理層指「不能再合作 (解僱)」。<br />\n<br />\n站長指出，公司員工守則規定站長當值不可留在站長室，但認為這次警告信及解僱事件，與新福利近期由內地增聘一批站長有關，批評公司在員工工作從未犯錯時，想出以此罪名炒本地人。本專頁已建議有關人士向工會或政府求助。<br />\n=========================<br />\n27/3 #新福利 #站長 #解僱 #外勞<br />\n<br />\n澳門真係仲衰過清朝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49bfaed32cb50b524eb7f65c021eb2aa7ee4a27","tid":611169,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd4dc36cdc3248399e7aca8e378b5bcb3eaa054","tid":611169,"uid":134474,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:20:11.000Z","msg":"小心有人入嚟咬你，然後屌鳩香港更不濟"},{"pid":"90998c3a434bc400be082528aed7ad1f818dc981","tid":611169,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c75fa7b2b34aa2258b2368bc3f69a1f4295e887","tid":611169,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:22:30.000Z","msg":"站長在工作時間留在站長室內<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"h